---
// SimoneCallout.astro
//
// "Built by / on the team's own production" callout for the homepage.
// Per v5 plan §4.1 (soft Option B): different visual register from the
// testimonial cards so the reader doesn't parse it as a fifth customer
// testimonial. Names Simone as a real person with skin in the game
// and routes to the case study.
---

<section class="simone-callout">
  <p class="callout-leadin">— and on the team's own production:</p>
  <p>
    <strong>Simone Scarduzio</strong> (founder, Beshu Tech) is migrating
    ReadonlyREST's 1.71 TB build catalog through DeltaGlider. The case
    study includes the bugs we hit (TMPDIR hardcoded in upstream, Traefik
    60s timeout, pipefail+head silent abort, EBS exhaustion) and how we
    fixed them.
  </p>
  <p>
    → <a href="/case-studies/readonlyrest-builds">Read the migration log</a>
  </p>
</section>

<style>
  .simone-callout {
    margin: 3rem 0;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--accent);
    background: var(--bg-soft);
    max-width: var(--measure-wide);
  }

  .callout-leadin {
    color: var(--ink-faint);
    font-style: italic;
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .simone-callout p {
    margin: 0.5rem 0;
  }
</style>
